title: Donald Trump Cancels 'Jimmy Kimmel Live' Appearance
text:
Donald Trump Cancels 'Jimmy Kimmel Li... Donald Trump Cancels 'Jimmy Kimmel Live' Appearance Next Story Prev Story 20 min ago Read more: Hollywood Reporter 
The real-estate mogul turned Republican presidential candidate was set to appear on Kimmel's Tuesday night episode, part of his week of shows from Brooklyn, and says he'll appear on a subsequent episode when the host's back in L.A. Donald Trump has canceled his appearance on Jimmy Kimmel Live , saying on Fox News that he has a "political event" Tuesday night and will appear on an episode of the ABC late-night show at a later date when it returns to L.A. "I have a political event, but I am going to do his show in two weeks," Trump said. "I have a big political event which I can't skip and I told him, I said, you know, 'I have this event; I can't skip it,' but I will be doing it in two weeks once I am out in Los Angeles."   Hollywood Reporter.
